<p begin="00:04:52.292" end="00:04:57.097" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; I WOULD LIKE TO BEGIN WITH </span><span style="block">THE COMPELLING STORY OF SARAH </span><span style="block">McKINLEY.</span></p>


<p begin="00:04:57.097" end="00:05:04.037" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">HOME ALONE WITH HER BABY SHE </span><span style="block">CALLED 911 WHEN TWO VIOLENT </span><span style="block">INTRUDERS BEGAN TO BREAK DOWN</span></p>


<p begin="00:05:04.037" end="00:05:06.073" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">HER FRONT DOOR.</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:06.073" end="00:05:11.545" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MS. McKINLEY FIRED HER WEAPON </span><span style="block">FATALLY WOUNDING ONE OF THE </span><span style="block">VIOLENT ATTACKERS.</span></p>


