<p begin="00:05:29.563" end="00:05:37.371" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MORE LIKELY TO BE HURT BY A GUN </span><span style="block">IN THE HOME THAN USE IT TO </span><span style="block">PROTECT FROM AN ASSAILANT.</span></p>


<p begin="00:05:37.371" end="00:05:45.379" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; QUICK QUESTION, SHE USED A </span><span style="block">REMINGTON 870-EXPRESS 12-GAIG </span><span style="block">SHOTGUN THAT WOULD NOT BE BANNED</span></p>


