<p begin="00:05:56.123" end="00:06:06.366" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU TOLD A JAMES JOYCEIAN STORY </span><span style="block">ABOUT THE LADY AND THE ROBBERS.</span></p>

<p begin="00:06:06.366" end="00:06:12.139" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU DON'T REMEMBER THE GUN, IE, </span><span style="block">THE ONLY DETAIL RELEVANT TO THE </span><span style="block">HEARING.</span></p>


<p begin="00:06:12.139" end="00:06:15.275" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IT WAS A NONBANNED WEAPON, A </span><span style="block">SHOTGUN.</span></p>

<p begin="00:06:15.275" end="00:06:16.877" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WHY DO YOU NEED AN AR-15.</span></p>
<p begin="00:06:16.877" end="00:06:26.453" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; THE PEACE OF MIND THAT A </span><span style="block">WOMAN HAS AS SHE'S FACING THREE, </span><span style="block">FOUR, FIVE VIOLENT ATTACKERS,</span></p>


<p begin="00:06:26.453" end="00:06:31.258" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">INTRUDERS IN HER HOME, WITH HER </span><span style="block">CHILDREN SCREAMING IN THE </span><span style="block">BACKGROUND, THE PEACE OF MIND</span></p>


<p begin="00:06:31.258" end="00:06:40.567" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">KNOWING SHE HAS A SCARY LOOKING </span><span style="block">GUN GIVES HER MORE COURAGE WHEN </span><span style="block">SHE'S FIGHTING HARDENED VIOLENT </span><span style="block">CRIMINALS.</span></p>



<p begin="00:06:40.567" end="00:06:46.406" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: WHEN DID IT TURN INTO </span><span style="block">THREE AND FOUR AND FIVE.</span></p>

<p begin="00:06:46.406" end="00:06:50.244" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">JEEZ, WHERE DID SHE LIVE THE </span><span style="block">ALAMO?</span></p>

<p begin="00:06:50.244" end="00:06:52.179" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?</span></p>
