<p begin="00:07:59.813" end="00:08:05.252" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">WHAT IS THIS THOU SHALT NOT </span><span style="block">KILL.</span></p>

<p begin="00:08:05.252" end="00:08:06.587" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MURDERERS WILL BYPASS THAT.</span></p>
